<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>snowpeak</title>
  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.3.min.js" integrity="sha256-pvPw+upLPUjgMXY0G+8O0xUf+/Im1MZjXxxgOcBQBXU=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/4fd2a00047.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/index.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/header.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/footer.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/reset.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%-include ('header.ejs')%>

  <div class="mainWrap">
      <div class="imgGroup">
          <div class="mainImg i1"></div>
          <div class="mainImg i2"></div>
          <div class="mainImg i3"></div>
      </div>
      <main>
        <div class="viewTitle">
            <div class="titleGroup">
                <h2 class="title1">New Products 2023 Snow peak</h2>
                <h2 class="title2">SEASON OFF and Special Offer JOIN NOW</h2>
                <h2 class="title3">HAPPY BLOG with SNOWPEAK</h2>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="viewP">
            <div class="pGroup">
                <p class="p1">Zekka/Multifunction Table Open Bamboo/Fastpack Entry Slepping System/Fire Blaster/Titanium Flask/ ShimoBarrel 160oz</p>
                <p class="p2">SEASON OFF we offer special discount for our members! join now!</p>
                <p class="p3">Share great moment with Snowpeak:)</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="viewBtn">
            <div class="btnGroup">
                <a href="/newitems"><button>Learn More</button></a>
                <a href="/login"><button>Join us</button></a>
                <a href="/community"><button>Click Event</button></a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carouselBtn">
          <div class="chevron chevronLft"><i class="fa-sharp fa-solid fa-circle-chevron-left"></i></div>
          <div class="circleGroup">
            <div class="circle c1"></div>
            <div class="circle c2"></div>
            <div class="circle c3"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="chevron chevronRgt"><i class="fa-sharp fa-solid fa-circle-chevron-right"></i></div>
          <div class="pause"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-pause"></i></div>
        </div>
      </main>
  </div>
  <div class="cntWrap">
      <div class="cnt content1">
          <header>
              <h2>Brand Story</h2>
              <h4>FROM Outdoor life style TO Outdoor life value</h4>
          </header>
          <section>
              <article>
                  <div class="image img1"></div>
                  <div class="texts">
                      <h3>쾌적 기준 수치</h3>
                      <p>모든 수치는 아웃도어 필드에서 최적의 쾌적함을 위한 수치입니다. 이 수치를 우리는”쾌적 기준 치수”라고 합니다. 서서 조리를 하는 하이 스타일은 지상고 830mm, 의자에 앉아 식사를 하는 미들 스타일은 지상고 660mm. 벤치에 앉아 BBQ를 즐기는 로우 스타일은 지상고 400mm, 땅에 직접 앉아(좌식) 조리나 식사를 즐길 수 있는 그라운드 스타일은 지상고 300mm의 기준 치수입니다.</p>
                  </div>
              </article>
              <article>
                  <div class="image img2"></div>
                  <div class="texts">
                      <h3>The Snow Peak Way</h3>
                      <p>우리 스노우피크는 개개인의 주체성이 가장 중요함을 자각하고, 같은 목표를 공유하며 진정한 신뢰를 바탕으로 힘을 합쳐 자연을 지향하는 라이프밸류를 제안합니다.</p>
                  </div>
              </article>
              <article>
                  <div class="image img3"></div>
                  <div class="texts">
                      <h3>스노우피크로 만나게 되는 우리 모두</h3>
                      <p>우리는 자연에서 연결됩니다. 스노우피크의 체험가치는 비로서 자연에서 실현됩니다.</p>
                    
                    </div>
              </article>
          </section>
      </div>
  </div>
  <div class="cntWrap">
    <div class="overgrid">

        <div class="cnt content2">
            <header>
                <h2>Product Line</h2>
                <h4>다양한 아웃도어 제품라인을 만나보실 수 있습니다.</h4>
            </header>
            <section>
                <article class="viewLft">
                    <div class="imgGroupLft">
                        <div class="image i1"></div>
                        <div class="image i2"></div>
                        <div class="image i3"></div>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="viewRgt">
                    <div class="imgGroupRgt">
                        <div class="image i1"></div>
                        <div class="image i2"></div>
                        <div class="image i3"></div>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <div class="chevronRgt">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right"></i>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="bnrWrap">
    <div class="image"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="cntWrap">
      <div class="cnt content3">
          <header>
              <h2>Our Recommendation</h2>
              <h4>한달간 인기가 많았던 제품들을 모아 추천해드립니다.</h4>
          </header>
          <div class="sectionView overflow">
            <section>
                <article>
                    <div class="viewItem">
                      <div class="image img1"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="texts">
                        <h3>Cotton Crewneck</h3>
                        <h5>148,000원</h5>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article>
                    <div class="viewItem">
                      <div class="image img2"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="texts">
                        <h3>Dry Boston Bag</h3>
                        <h5>100,000원</h5>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article>
                    <div class="viewItem">
                      <div class="image img3"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="texts">
                        <h3>타쿠바코 브라운</h3>
                        <h5>218,000원</h5>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article>
                    <div class="viewItem">
                      <div class="image img4"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="texts">
                        <h3>그랜드오프톤 싱글1000</h3>
                        <h5>778,000원</h5>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article>
                    <div class="viewItem">
                      <div class="image img5"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="texts">
                        <h3>우산 그레이</h3>
                        <h5>64,000원</h5>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article>
                    <div class="viewItem">
                      <div class="image img6"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="texts">
                        <h3>티탄싱글머그300</h3>
                        <h5>30,000원</h5>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article>
                    <div class="viewItem">
                      <div class="image img7"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="texts">
                        <h3>토야2</h3>
                        <h5>423,000원</h5>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article>
                    <div class="viewItem">
                      <div class="image img8"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="texts">
                        <h3>타케비 립스톱 셔츠</h3>
                        <h5>168,000원</h5>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article>
                    <div class="viewItem">
                      <div class="image img9"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="texts">
                        <h3>타키비 데님 베스트</h3>
                        <h5>430,000원</h5>
                    </div>
                </article>
              </section>
          </div>
            <button>More Products</button>
      </div>
  </div>
  <div class="cntWrap">
      <div class="cnt content4">
          <header>
              <h2>Community</h2>
          </header>
          <section>
            <div class="atcGroup">
               <% for(var i =0; i<blogpost.length; i++) { %>
                <a href="/detail/<%=blogpost[i]._id%>">
                   <article>
                       <div class="image" style="background-image:url(/public/image/<%=blogpost[i]._id%>.jpg)"></div>
                       <div class="texts">
                           <h3><%=blogpost[i].title%></h3>
                           <h5><%=blogpost[i].details%></h5>
                       </div>
                   </article>
                </a>
               <% } %>
            </div>
            </section>
            <div class="chevron">
              <div class="chevronLft"><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-left"></i></div>
              <div class="chevronRgt"><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right"></i></div>
            </div>
      </div>
  </div>

  
  <%-include ('footer.html')%>

<script src="/js/index.js"></script>
</body>
</html>